DaynaPORT SCSI/Link Linux 7.x driver -- change history

0.2  2026-06-16
     - RX: poll continuously while frames are arriving -- the poll loop skips its
       wait and issues the next READ(6) immediately when the previous one
       returned data, falling back to the cadence timer only on an empty poll.
     - New debug module parameter (off by default, runtime-writable): logs
       per-READ RX yield and rate every 256 READs.

0.1  2026-06-15
     Initial release.